* {{ill|Kanbun (era)|ja|寛文|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 12 ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1672|ja|1672nd year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|June 8|ja|6月8日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – The {{ill|Shōkōkan|ja|彰考館|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} is established at the Mito Domain residence in Koishikawa, advancing the compilation of the {{ill|Dai Nihonshi|ja|大日本史|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} .
