== Deaths ==
* {{ill|Bunsei (era)|ja|文政|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 12 (Gregorian {{ill|1829|ja|1829th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|June 14|ja|6月14日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Matsudaira Sadanobu|ja|松平定信|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , senior councilor (rōjū) of the Tokugawa shogunate and architect of the {{ill|Kansei Reforms|ja|Kanseiの改革|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (* {{ill|1758|ja|1758th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ).
== Commemorations ==
* '''Bamboo Drunken Day''' (竹酔日, *Chikusuibi*) – A Chinese folk belief that this day is the best for transplanting bamboo. It is said that the bamboo is "drunk" and unaware of being moved, allowing it to root well. Also known as '''Bamboo Bewilderment Day''' (竹迷日), '''Dragon Birth Day''' (竜生日), or '''Bamboo Birth Day''' (竹誕日).
